  <data key="d9">"Java class key sequence direct located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.direct. Uses related classes key block. Defines methods alloc new block, get next id."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The KeySequenceDirect class is responsible for managing a sequence of IDs, providing methods to allocate new blocks and retrieve the next ID in the sequence. It appears to be a component of a larger system, possibly related to key block management, as indicated by its package and related class KeyBlock."</data>
