  <data key="d9">"Java class key block located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util. Uses related classes key block iterator. Defines methods key block, list iterator, size."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The KeyBlock class is responsible for managing a collection of keys, providing methods to iterate over the keys and retrieve the number of keys. It likely serves as a container or a data structure for storing and accessing key values."</data>
