<node id="class:com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.QuoteDataBean">
  <data key="d0">"class:com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.QuoteDataBean"</data>
  <data key="d1">"QuoteDataBean"</data>
  <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
  <data key="d3">"Clase QuoteDataBean"</data>
  <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
  <data key="d5">{"archivo": "monoliths/daytrader/QuoteDataBean.java"}</data>
  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class quote data bean located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities. Uses related classes quote data bean. Defines methods equals, get change, get company name, get high, get low, get open, get price, get random instance, get symbol, get volume, hash code, print, quote data bean, set change, set company name, set high, set low, set open, set price, set symbol, set volume, to html, to string."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The QuoteDataBean class is responsible for managing quote data, providing getter and setter methods for various attributes such as price, high, low, open, and volume, as well as methods for comparing instances and converting the data to HTML."</data>
