  <data key="d9">"Java class holding data bean located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities. Uses related classes account data bean, holding data bean, quote data bean. Defines methods equals, get account, get holding id, get purchase date, get purchase price, get quantity, get quote, get quote id, get random instance, hash code, holding data bean, print, set account, set holding id, set purchase date, set purchase price, set quantity, set quote, set quote id, to html, to string."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The HoldingDataBean class is responsible for managing holding data, providing access to and modification of attributes such as account, holding ID, purchase date, price, quantity, and quote information. It offers various operations to retrieve and update this data, as well as convert it to HTML and string representations."</data>
