  <data key="d9">"Java class log located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util. Defines methods debug, do action trace, do debug, do stat, do trace, error, get action trace, get trace, log, print, print collection, print object, set action trace, set trace, stat, trace, trace enter, trace exit."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The Log class is responsible for managing logging operations, providing methods to log messages at various levels (debug, trace, error, etc.) and to print data in different formats. It offers control over logging levels and trace actions."</data>
