<node id="class:com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util.CompleteOrderThread">
  <data key="d0">"class:com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util.CompleteOrderThread"</data>
  <data key="d1">"CompleteOrderThread"</data>
  <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
  <data key="d3">"Clase CompleteOrderThread"</data>
  <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
  <data key="d5">{"archivo": "monoliths/daytrader/CompleteOrderThread.java"}</data>
  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class complete order thread located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util. Uses related classes trade direct, trade services. Defines methods complete order thread, run."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CompleteOrderThread class is responsible for managing order completion operations, providing a thread-based execution mechanism. It appears to be a utility class used in the daytrader application, possibly interacting with TradeDirect and TradeServices classes."</data>
