  <data key="d9">"Java class trade slsblocal located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.ejb3. Inherits from trade services. Uses related classes quote data bean. Defines methods investment return, ping two phase, publish quote price change."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The TradeSLSBLocal class is responsible for managing trade-related operations, providing methods to calculate investment return, and notifying price changes for quote data. It likely interacts with QuoteDataBean and TradeServices classes to perform these operations."</data>
