  <data key="d9">"Java class market summary singleton located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.ejb3. Uses related classes market summary data bean, quote data bean. Defines methods get market summary data bean, set market summary data bean, setup, update market summary."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The MarketSummarySingleton class is responsible for managing a single instance of market summary data, providing operations to retrieve and update this data. It maintains a reference to a MarketSummaryDataBean instance, which is used to store and retrieve market summary information."</data>
