  <data key="d9">"Java class market summary data bean located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.beans. Uses related classes market summary data bean, quote data bean. Defines methods get gain percent, get open tsia, get random instance, get summary date, get top gainers, get top losers, get tsia, get volume, market summary data bean, print, set open tsia, set summary date, set top gainers, set top losers, set tsia, set volume, to html, to json, to string."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The MarketSummaryDataBean class is responsible for managing market summary data, providing operations to access and modify its attributes such as gain percent, open time series index, and volume. It also offers methods to retrieve top gainers and losers, as well as convert its data to various formats like HTML and JSON."</data>
