  <data key="d9">"Java class account profile data bean located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities. Uses related classes account data bean, account profile data bean. Defines methods account profile data bean, equals, get account, get address, get credit card, get email, get full name, get password, get random instance, get user id, hash code, print, set account, set address, set credit card, set email, set full name, set password, set user id, to html, to string."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The AccountProfileDataBean class is responsible for managing an account profile, providing access to and modification of its attributes such as account, address, credit card, email, full name, and user ID. It offers methods to retrieve and update these attributes, as well as to generate a random instance and convert the data to HTML or string representations."</data>
