  <data key="d9">"Java class financial utils located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util. Uses related classes holding data bean. Defines methods compute gain, compute gain percent, compute holdings total, print change html, print gain html, print gain percent html, print quote link."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The FinancialUtils class is responsible for managing financial calculations and data presentation, providing methods to compute gains, holdings totals, and generate HTML output for financial data. It appears to work in conjunction with the HoldingDataBean class to perform these operations."</data>
