  <data key="d9">"Java class dtbroker3 mdb located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.ejb3. Uses related classes mdbstats, timer stat, trade direct, trade services, trade slsblocal. Defines methods dtbroker3 mdb, get trade, on message."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The DTBroker3MDB class is responsible for managing trades and providing operations to retrieve trade information. It appears to be a message-driven bean (MDB) that handles incoming messages and interacts with related classes such as TradeDirect and TradeServices."</data>
