  <data key="d9">"Java class mdbstats located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util. Uses related classes mdbstats, timer stat. Defines methods add timing, get instance, mdbstats, reset."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The MDBStats class is responsible for managing timing statistics, providing methods to add timing data and reset the statistics. It appears to be a singleton class, offering a getInstance method for accessing its instance."</data>
