  <data key="d9">"Java class key block iterator located in package com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util. Defines methods add, has next, has previous, next, next index, previous, previous index, remove, set."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The KeyBlockIterator class is responsible for managing a sequence of elements, providing operations to traverse and modify the sequence, including adding, removing, and accessing elements at specific indices. It supports bidirectional iteration, allowing for both forward and backward navigation through the sequence."</data>
